      "role": "user",
      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>it's just not that simple. people say that but they don't get it. they don't understand what it's like to realize you have nothing left to offer the world. no way to fix this. no way to climb back up. it feels like i've just reached the end of my rope and everything is just... quiet and empty now. it feels more honest to just accept it than to pretend there's a way out.",
