      "content": "it just feels like putting a bandaid on a gunshot wound. people keep saying things will get better but they're just saying what they think i want to hear. the truth is that the version of me that could actually function is dead. i'm just a ghost in a life that doesn't exist anymore. doesn't it just seem more peaceful to stop fighting something that's already over?",
